text: The Armenian Air Force is the aerial group of the Armed Forces of Armenia. It was a part of the military reform program of Ter-Grigoriants. Armenian anti- aircraft defense has an anti-aircraft missile brigade and two regiments armed with 100 missile launchers of various models and fixes. These missile launchers include the M79 Osa, Krug, S-75, S-125, and S-300. There are also 24 Scud ballistic missiles with eight launchers. ==Related pages== *Armed Forces of Armenia == Other websites == *Russia is satisfied with Armeniaâ€™s air defense capabilities.
